column5: Got up to the camp for three nights with Monique, Jaden and Jaden's good friend Summer. heres some quick pictures!!  The water is WAY down.. my floating dock.. well it aint floting... The rivers better below us though cause there's a dam.    The fish were on... this great year class of pike were everywhere.. and getting bigger every year!!          Double header!!              We even caught a small pickeral on the troll which Summer chowed on!!    Great weekend with two great bush girllzzz..
I see Jaden has the same pike hold as mommy, and that Summer doesn't like to hold fish  Nice report Teej, looks like you all had a great time.  Joey
Beauty shot of the double header! What make are those poppers?
Looks like a fine time boss. Damn (dam) that river is low!
looks like a great had by all next time summer has to hold a fish
Good stuff, TJ...looks like a couple more "fishing queens" in the making!!
damn. nice fish, also that little pike is the "little pike that could" would be a gold mine for a kids book or show
